{"tid":2274404,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"零售業年關難過 全港失業率恐破七","createTime":"2020-11-06T11:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T12:52:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"89ab3236f8107f9155f7f598edfd9879c406a30c","tid":2274404,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:56:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/P5QUD77EVBELTL66TTKS3GW3UQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FP5QUD77EVBELTL66TTKS3GW3UQ%2F&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9gwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=f1ef3f66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FP5QUD77EVBELTL66TTKS3GW3UQ%2F&h=6f65feed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/P5QUD77EVBELTL66TTKS3GW3UQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n零售業年關難過 全港失業率恐破七<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/19PTAgluWGq-DYe5HyPIPi6EfCc=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/T3PQI6QJYBHTFEQO4MLU32HWII.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F19PTAgluWGq-DYe5HyPIPi6EfCc%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FT3PQI6QJYBHTFEQO4MLU32HWII.jpg&h=38be535b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李兆波<br />\n<br />\n疫情反覆令經濟疲弱，百業蕭條。香港總商會8月以問卷訪問231家企業，結果顯示，政府若不推出新一輪的紓困措施，超過四成受訪的中小企及近四分一大企業最多只能支撐6個月。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：社會專題：保就業斷纜 疫市工彈起  區區天光墟 失業大軍搞旺地攤經濟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n銷售額跌140億<br />\n<br />\n有學者指出沒有保就業「吊命」，「下一滴血」將為零售業打工仔，加上不少公司的年終結算為3月底，很大機會在12月起逐漸裁員：「12月、1月有幾個大節日，聖誕、元旦、農曆年，如果政府唔做嘢，個市會好慘淡，出面血流成河！」<br />\n<br />\n政府公佈9月最新數據，本港零售業銷貨額由去年中每月平均400億元插水至260億元，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他續指，部份企業在12月或3月的年度結算亦影響裁員決定，他舉例，國泰在每年最。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"596905cd371043768be64f7f303a1b2b9f96d8b8","tid":2274404,"uid":191107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T11:57:02.000Z","msg":"虛火黎姐"},{"pid":"889bc274b71a1855cbf73ae0bbc7c6de7e0c3727","tid":2274404,"uid":253016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:15:46.000Z","msg":"小小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成堆垃圾零技術知識工<br />\n下年等破20"},{"pid":"fed21b8de1796c2784d65538ea76d302bc5844d7","tid":2274404,"uid":25794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最衰佔中"}]}